transcript:
Customer: Assalam Walekum kya haal hai aap sabhi ka ye bata dijiye.
Executive: Ha thik hai.
Customer: Aasif bhai main ye keh raha hu main aapko call kar raha hu actually whatsapp calling se kar raha tha na to usme number add nahi ho sakta ya to google meet pe aa jayenge aap inse baat kariye.
Executive: Google meet pe aa jayenge aap?
Customer: Ab inse baat kariye ek kaam kariye.
Executive: Thik hai thik hai thik hai google meet pe aap aayenge main ye puch raha hu abhi aapse.
Customer: Ho jayega main abhi main namaz pe ja raha hu.
Executive: Achcha are nahi thik hai thik hai aap namaz padh lo thik hai fir main call karta hu tab tak free ho.
Customer: Aap inko call kar dijiye fir main aapse aake puchta hu.
Executive: Thik hai thik hai thik hai okay.
Customer: Thik hai.
